&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have experience supporting external audits related to revenue recognition&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bring a background in Accounting or Finance, combined with systems expertise&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have familiarity with data warehouse integrations for revenue reporting and analytics&lt;/p&gt;
